# Harness Rule

Todo cambio sigue:

Requirement → Spec → Plan → Tests → Implementation → Validation → Review → Human Approval.

Prohibido saltar tests en bugs.
Prohibido implementar feature significativa sin spec.
Prohibido cerrar tarea con pipeline fallido.
